### Get all notifications for a user
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/notifications?userId=1

### Get unread notifications only
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/notifications?userId=1&unreadOnly=true

### Get notifications with pagination
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/notifications?userId=1&limit=5&offset=0

### Optional environment defaults for IntelliJ HTTP Client
### @name env
@host=localhost
@port=8080
